user_description: Mental Health Survivor ❤️ Interdisciplinary student @Stanford. Comms: @TFGH + @StanfordAlumni. 3X-50 Mile Runner. Opinions my own.
text:
The #CovidVaccine is miraculously effective.

The FDA set a benchmark for a vax that was 50% effective. Against flu, efficacy is 45%.

We produced one 90% effective against several variants of a more deadly disease within 1 year 😮

There's no question: it works. @Voices4Vaccines

I know that many of us are tired and frustrated but being hostile towards those still uncertain re: #CovidVaccine is not the way.
Patience & Empathy are still needed. Calling people names is counterproductive & rude.
We need each other to get out of this pandemic. #COVID19
